<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.5.5">
<l>ēḻu māmaran tuḷaipaṭac cilaivaḷait tilaṅkaiyai malaṅkuvitta</l>
<l>āḻi yāṉṉamak karuḷiya varuḷoṭum pakalellai kaḻikiṉṟatāl</l>
<l>tōḻi nāmitaṟ keṉceytun tuṇaiyillai cuṭarpaṭu mutunīril</l>
<l>āḻa vāḻkiṉṟa vāviyai yaṭuvatō rantivan taṭaikiṉṟatē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The grace that the discus bearer, who causes trouble for Laṅkā,</l>
<l rend="indent">having bent the bow so that seven great trees were pierced,</l>
<l>Bestowed on us and the limits of the day are slipping away!</l>
<l>Friend, what do we do for this? There is no help!</l>
<l rend="indent">As the sun sinks over vast flooded fields,</l>
<l>The destroyer of [my] living breath, the evening twilight,</l>
<l rend="indent">appears and closes in.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
